# MantTeq Website Documentation

## Project Structure
/
├── index.html          # Main website file
├── styles/
│   └── index.css       # Main stylesheet
├── scripts/
│   └── index.js        # Main JavaScript file
├── assets/             # All media assets
│   ├── images/         # Image files
│   └── logo/           # Logo files
└── thank_you.html      # Thank you page

## Technical Specifications
- Built with HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript
- Responsive design (mobile-first approach)
- Form handling via Formspree
- Optimized for performance (lazy loading, service worker)

## Features
1. Responsive Carousel
2. Service Modals
3. FAQ Accordion
4. Contact Form with Validation
5. Smooth Scrolling
6. Back-to-Top Button
7. Newsletter Subscription

## Deployment
1. Hosted on GitHub Pages
2. Custom domain can be configured via CNAME
3. Automatic deployment on push to main branch

## Maintenance
- Update content by editing HTML files
- Update styles in CSS file
- Update functionality in JavaScript file
- Test changes locally before pushing